Member ---- UC_Transaction
Member ---- UC_Browse
Member ---- UC_ViewHistory
Member ---- UC_ExportHistory
Member ---- UC_Rating
Member ---- UC_ViewNotification
Member ---- UC_Forum
Member ---- UC_Chat
Member ---- UC_Account
Member ---- UC_Verify

